OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781294762
OL,3,CChild killer stabbed 25 times in his
OL,4,Ccell
OL,6,FA convicted child killer was stabbed
OL,7,F25 times in his high-security prison
OL,8,Fcell at HMP Wakefield and left to
OL,9,Fbleed to death in his bed, a jury was
OL,10,Ftold.
OL,12,FThe murder trial of three fellow
OL,13,Finmates, Mark Fellows, 45, Lee Newell,
OL,14,F57, and David Taylor, 64, accused of
OL,15,Fmurdering 33-year-old Kyle Bevan
OL,16,Fopened at Leeds Crown Court on
OL,17,FWednesday, 10 June.
OL,19,FBevan was serving a life-sentence for
OL,20,Fthe murder of his partner's two-year-
OL,21,Fold daughter Lola James in July 2020.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
