FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781294762
OL,3,CChild killer stabbed 25 times in his
OL,4,Ccell
OL,6,FProsecutor Jason Pitter KC showed
OL,7,Fjurors CCTV footage from November 4
OL,8,Flast year, capturing Bevan entering
OL,9,Fhis cell on the wing's fourth landing.
OL,10,FThe three defendants then followed him
OL,11,Finside.
OL,13,F"It was four minutes and 39 seconds
OL,14,Flater that those three left Bevan's
OL,15,Fcell together, as if nothing had
OL,16,Fhappened. Bevan did not. They left as
OL,17,Fif nothing had happened."
OL,19,FHe was discovered the following
OL,20,Fmorning when it was found he had bled
OL,21,Fto death.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
