OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781294762
OL,3,CChild killer stabbed 25 times in his
OL,4,Ccell
OL,6,FThe court heard that Bevan was
OL,7,Fviolently stabbed inside, with 25
OL,8,Fwounds which penetrated his jugular
OL,9,Fvein, aorta and heart.
OL,11,FHe sustained over 30 injuries in
OL,12,Ftotal, which suggested another pointed
OL,13,Fweapon had been used.
OL,15,FMr Pitter said a folded piece of metal
OL,16,Fwas later found, which had been made
OL,17,Ffrom a piece of a television, which
OL,18,Fhad Bevan's blood on it.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781294762
OL,3,CChild killer stabbed 25 times in his
OL,4,Ccell
OL,6,FThe prosecutor told the court that all
OL,7,Fthree of the accused were sentences
OL,8,Ffor offences including murder. Fellows
OL,9,Fis serving life sentences for two
OL,10,Fcounts of murder and conspiracy to
OL,11,Fcause really serious harm.
OL,13,FNewell was serving a life sentence for
OL,14,Fmurder and previously "expressed a
OL,15,Fdislike of vulnerable prisoners".
OL,26,@vD@WOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
