CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781294762
OL,3,CChild killer stabbed 25 times in his
OL,4,Ccell
OL,6,FAll three men accused deny murder.
OL,8,FThe trial, which is expected to last
OL,9,Fthree weeks, was adjourned until
OL,10,FThursday.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/7
